HOW Spring Boot Connects to Database

Spring Boot uses:

Spring Data JPA → Hibernate → Database

Controller → Service → Repository → JPA → Hibernate → Database

application.properties (Database Configuration)

This file tells Spring:

Which database?
Username?
Password?
URL?

